title: 820-00165 light orange, so press the power for a while and it is slow.
message:
Hello friend, this mac has already been repaired by a third party, a broken track has been redone that connects PP3v42_g3h to pin 8 of the u1950 and u7870 appears to be already exchanged because it had flow around it.

Voltages: PPBUS_g3h 8.59v and PP3v42_g3h 3.40v and PP5v_s0 only when the machine turns on.
